      "readmeHtml": "<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h1 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">CUDA Flood Fill - Evolution Roadmap</h1><a id=\"user-content-cuda-flood-fill---evolution-roadmap\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: CUDA Flood Fill - Evolution Roadmap\" href=\"#cuda-flood-fill---evolution-roadmap\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Vision</strong>: Demonstrate the evolution from simple sequential CPU algorithms to complex parallel GPU implementations</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h2 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Project Philosophy</h2><a id=\"user-content-project-philosophy\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Project Philosophy\" href=\"#project-philosophy\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">This project showcases the journey from simple to complex, sequential to parallel:</p>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li><strong>Start Simple</strong>: Begin with a basic CPU BFS that anyone can understand</li>\n<li><strong>Add Complexity</strong>: Show how more sophisticated algorithms (scan) work on CPU</li>\n<li><strong>Introduce Parallelism</strong>: Move the simple algorithm to GPU</li>\n<li><strong>Optimize</strong>: Combine the best of both worlds (GPU + advanced algorithms)</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h2 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Evolution Path (The Main Story)</h2><a id=\"user-content-evolution-path-the-main-story\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Evolution Path (The Main Story)\" href=\"#evolution-path-the-main-story\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<div class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"><h3 class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\">Stage 1: <strong>CPU Sequential - Single Blob BFS</strong> 🌱</h3><a id=\"user-content-stage-1-cpu-sequential---single-blob-bfs-\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Stage 1: CPU Sequential - Single Blob BFS 🌱\" href=\"#stage-1-cpu-sequential---single-blob-bfs-\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Goal</strong>: Create the simplest possible flood-fill implementation\n<strong>Status</strong>: ✅ <strong>COMPLETED</strong></p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><strong>Algorithm</strong>: Basic Breadth-First Search (BFS) for a single blob</li>\n<li><strong>Platform</strong>: CPU (Sequential)</li>\n<li><strong>Focus</strong>: Clarity and correctness</li>\n<li><strong>Implementation</strong>: <code>src/cpu/sequential.py</code> (single blob portion)</li>\n<li><strong>Key Learning"
